@@yQuarantine Ledger, Archive Passage West@@N~
@@yA connecting passage between the Quarantine Ledger complex and the main Assessment Courtyard zone allows monitoring staff to rotate between their post and the main Ledger Quarter without traversing the full corridor network.@@N The passage is deliberately plain — no archive material is stored here, no decoration applied — since this is a movement corridor only. @@yThe contrast with the document-dense main archive lanes is sharp; this passage is intentionally empty to ensure that nothing is inadvertently moved between the containment zone and the general archive.@@N Air movement in this passage is faster than in the main corridors, drawn by the ventilation differential between the Quarantine complex and the rest of the Ledger Quarter.
